name: hopAppNishiuraTravel
description:
The Hands-on Portal Travel application loader is used to load the Webbles necessary for the Travel application developed for the Hands-on Portal project.

This Webble will also react to resizing of the browser window and try to resize and move the visualization Webbles around to fit the new browser window size.
